sec.p:
Both anthraquinone and anthracene are semi-volatile organic compounds that can be present in the atmosphere in gaseous and particulate phase. The partitioning between the gaseous and particulate phase depends on ambient atmospheric conditions such as temperature and aerosol concentration. The mass fraction in the particulate phase is given by θ=cp/(cp+cg)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
